Class TablesPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JSplitPane
            • gui.tables.TablesPane
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class TablesPane
extends javax.swing.JSplitPane
    Extension of JSplitPane class. It splits the tab of the TabbedPane if a table has children. Top half is the parent table, bottom half is a TabbedPane with child tables.
    Author:
    Milan Radeta
